videos.headline: UAB celebrates AAC win after triumphing over Temple
videos.description: Confetti goes airborne after UAB celebrates a convincing 85-69 win over Temple in the American Athletic Conference championship.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (UAB celebrates AAC win after triumphing over Temple) 2024/03/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Eric Gaines' wild pass is rewarded with a triple
videos.description: Eric Gaines swings it to Alejandro Vasquez, who drains the open triple for UAB.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Eric Gaines' wild pass is rewarded with a triple) 2024/03/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hysier Miller's steal turns into an and-1 bucket
videos.description: Hysier Miller gets the steal on the other end, then he makes a pass to Shane Dezonie for the and-1 layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Hysier Miller's steal turns into an and-1 bucket) 2024/03/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Jordan Riley cleans up the miss with a putback slam
videos.description: Jordan Riley is assertive in the paint as he gets the board and slam for Temple.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Jordan Riley cleans up the miss with a putback slam) 2024/03/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Yaxel Lendeborg swats away Eric Gaines' layup
videos.description: Yaxel Lendeborg executes a nice defensive play with this block on Eric Gaines' layup attempt.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Yaxel Lendeborg swats away Eric Gaines' layup) 2024/03/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Yaxel Lendeborg is relentless inside to score this deuce
videos.description: Yaxel Lendeborg misses his first shot but immediately gets his rebound and sinks the and-1 layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Yaxel Lendeborg is relentless inside to score this deuce) 2024/03/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Christian Coleman gets the breakaway slam to go
videos.description: Christian Coleman has an open lane to the basket as he goes up for a nice transition jam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Christian Coleman gets the breakaway slam to go) 2024/03/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hysier Miller gets to the middle for the and-1 bucket
videos.description: Hysier Miller uses a Eurostep to get the and-1 basket to go.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Hysier Miller gets to the middle for the and-1 bucket) 2024/03/17 ESHEET

videos.headline: Javian Davis gets the ball up quick for the and-1 shot
videos.description: Despite the contact, Javian Davis scores the and-1 bucket inside.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Javian Davis gets the ball up quick for the and-1 shot) 2024/03/17 ESHEET
